{"tid":2331736,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英還柙｜肥佬黎赤柱監獄度過最凍一夜 畢明：佢叫大家頂住","createTime":"2020-12-19T04:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T05:12:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"47d085157ffb16c521c560feb0ae3382d871701a","tid":2331736,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T04:53:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201219/MSP4YUFZJNHFNGJY72ZMKFE5CU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201219%2FMSP4YUFZJNHFNGJY72ZMKFE5CU%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBRQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=f1aa539e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201219%2FMSP4YUFZJNHFNGJY72ZMKFE5CU%2F&h=b3a5b480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201219/MSP4YUFZJNHFNGJY72ZMKFE5CU/</a><br />\n<br />\n黎智英還柙｜肥佬黎赤柱監獄度過最凍一夜 畢明：佢叫大家頂住<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被指違反工業邨用地租賃條款，本月3日被控欺詐解上法庭，還柙候訊；在等候申請保釋之際，復遭警方國安處引用港版國安法，起訴他另一條勾結外國或境外勢力危害國家安全罪的罪名，被解往西九龍裁判法院提堂，結果遭國安法指定法官、裁判官蘇惠德下令要還柙至明年4月16日再訊。黎智英本來被關進荔枝角收押所，昨天（18日）懲教署突然將他轉到高度設防的赤柱監獄繼續還柙。今日是被收押的第17天，黎智英的女兒與專欄作家畢明，冒着寒冷天氣警告到赤柱探望。<br />\n<br />\n根據天文台記錄，今日錄得赤柱最低溫為13.2&deg;C。寒風颯颯，早上9時許，黎的女兒與畢明先後到達赤柱監獄，然後一同進入探望，至早上10時50分左右離開。黎女引述黎生稱，這裏的氣溫和荔枝角差不多，也有足夠被鋪，黎女說：「佢情況ok、精神都幾好...佢話大家同事好辛苦，呢排《蘋果》啲同事都好辛苦，好appreciate（欣賞），好appreciate大家咁努力。」<br />\n<br />\n畢明補充說：「黎生叫大家頂住。佢好好呀，佢話唔知點解突然間睇睇吓書，或者做緊乜嘢，會突然間好開心，自己喺度笑，我諗佢相信自己做啲啱嘅嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n台灣台北市長柯文哲接受訪問時形容，黎智英身為大商家，寧可放棄攜錢出走，也要堅持理念留港，是很有氣魄。他又指看到黎的被捕、被警方鎖上鐵鏈手銬的照片，只會激起台灣更大的反中情緒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5ik2Xrwx1uBfDFvceGXixXP32Mo=/4365x3023/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YLWIEKTQ3JDETFTUAUSFGBO4BU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5ik2Xrwx1uBfDFvceGXixXP32Mo%3D%2F4365x3023%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYLWIEKTQ3JDETFTUAUSFGBO4BU.jpg&h=4c156b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兩人見面即擁抱相聚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RX9fV_8AhxJTQk8y72GQOgQzwUU=/5608x3843/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6V32DGILAZFVNE5DLQ7ON2R6TY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRX9fV_8AhxJTQk8y72GQOgQzwUU%3D%2F5608x3843%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6V32DGILAZFVNE5DLQ7ON2R6TY.jpg&h=d2d45a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畢明指黎生從容面對。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/krhgs-wlo9blG2IVClPbHgDKUsk=/5394x3812/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4KLOTRPTSFD2HHJXNEHCG243M4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fkrhgs-wlo9blG2IVClPbHgDKUsk%3D%2F5394x3812%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4KLOTRPTSFD2HHJXNEHCG243M4.jpg&h=b958829d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NMkxY4LwZmLbV_CJu02xO_yfFhY=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZLMMKHYHPZGIZIS2RX2P6MLYNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNMkxY4LwZmLbV_CJu02xO_yfFhY%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZLMMKHYHPZGIZIS2RX2P6MLYNE.jpg&h=ac4af044&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎智英昨日被懲教署帶離荔枝角收押所，前往赤柱監獄繼續收柙。資料圖片<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 立即WhatsApp 《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線 或致電：63836568<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》英文版免費試睇：了解更多<br />\n<br />\n英文版已登錄《蘋果》App，立即下載/ 更新：iOS / Android<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n支持蘋果深度報道，深入社區，踢爆權貴，即Like蘋果專題及調查組FB專頁！"},{